    <summary>Allows you to obtain the full path of the source file that contains the caller. This is the file path at the time of compile.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 You apply the `CallerFilePath` attribute to an optional parameter that has a default value. You must specify an explicit default value for the optional parameter. You can't apply this attribute to parameters that aren't specified as optional.  
  
 For more information, see [Caller Information](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/9cb2b8c0-c4f6-44b8-9c90-38948455b373).  
  
   
  
